      • deletePartButtonPushed

        void deletePartButtonPushed()
        This method deletes a selected part in the Parts Table. This method is called when a part is selected and the delete part button is pushed. A feature that would be useful to implement in the future, would be to allow multiple selected parts deleted at the same time, rather than having to do so one by one.
